textfsm_template:
Value INTERFACE (\S+\.\d+)
Value INDEX (Index\s\d+)
Value SNMP_IFINDEX (SNMP ifIndex\s\d+)
Value PRIMARY_IP (Primary IP Address\s\S+)
Value ADMIN_STATUS (Admin status\s\S+)
Value INPUT_ERRORS (\d+)
Value INPUT_DROPS (\d+)
Value INPUT_STSECOND (\d+)
Value INPUT_PROTOCOL_DROPS (\d+)
Value OUTPUT_ERRORS (\d+)
Value OUTPUT_DROPS (\d+)
Value OUTPUT_STSECOND (\d+)
Value OUTPUT_PROTOCOL_DROPS (\d+)

Start
  ^Logical Interface ${INTERFACE}\s+\(${INDEX}\)\s+\(${SNMP_IFINDEX}\)\s+\(${PRIMARY_IP}\)\s+\(${ADMIN_STATUS}\)\s*$$
  ^\s+Input errors:\s*$$
  ^\s+Errors:\s+${INPUT_ERRORS},\s+Drops:\s+${INPUT_DROPS},\s+Stsecond:\s+${INPUT_STSECOND},\s+Protocol drops:\s+${INPUT_PROTOCOL_DROPS}\s*$$
  ^\s+Output errors:\s*$$
  ^\s+Errors:\s+${OUTPUT_ERRORS},\s+Drops:\s+${OUTPUT_DROPS},\s+Stsecond:\s+${OUTPUT_STSECOND},\s+Protocol drops:\s+${OUTPUT_PROTOCOL_DROPS}\s*$$ -> Record
